      "date": "2024-01-24 20:26:38.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nLND level timeouts are necessary for correctly tuning timeouts on LNet routers that bridge network types with different timeout characteristics as well as on clients/servers that have multiple network types. As such, this patch should be abandoned.",
