        "committer": {
          "name": "Amir Shehata",
          "email": "ashehata@whamcloud.com",
          "date": "2019-12-05 23:51:19.000000000",
          "tz": -480
        },
        "subject": "LU-13020 o2iblnd: timeout is now obsolete",
        "message": "LU-13020 o2iblnd: timeout is now obsolete\n\nThe LND timeout is now determined as a function of the\nlnet_transaction_timeout module parameter:\n\nif lnet_retry_count > 0 &&\n   lnet_transaction_timeout > lnet_retry_count\n   lnd_timeout = lnet_transaction_timeout / lnet_retry_count\nelse\n   lnd_timeout = lnet_transaction_timeout\n\nFor more details please look at:\n  api-ni.c:retry_count_set()\nand\n  api-ni.c:transaction_to_set()\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Amir Shehata <ashehata@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Id4a50c7e5e2cd7660f3f6614a28099d7487254f0\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
